{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9804c6fe10","title":"中央文革“2·24”对西藏文革的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2fbd0be291","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":24,"articleId":"9804c6fe10","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"张国华","id":"0faca0c469","type":"人物"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"87dfa5c6ff","name":"中央文革"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c051be7be6","type":"title","text":"中央文革“2·24”对西藏文革的指示中央文革","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0416ac238d","type":"paragraph","text":"拉萨革命造反总部、拉萨革命造反公社、首都赴藏革命造反总部、首都三司驻藏联络站、北航“红旗”小分队等各民族革命造反派：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a916d91c5a","type":"paragraph","text":"我们收到你们2月22日从拉萨发来的电报。对你们提出的问题，答复如下：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"693d9dabd7","type":"paragraph","text":"一、中央军委2月12日给西藏军区的电报，是代表毛主席、党中央的意见的。中央文化革命小组完全拥护这个电报所说的：张国华同志是站在毛主席路线一边的，尽管他在工作上有缺点和错误，但基本上是个好同志。望军区党委同志向革命群众做些工作。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"45a0188e02","type":"paragraph","text":"二、中央文化革命小组，欢迎你们要掌握斗争大方向，捍卫和实现伟大领袖毛主席提出的革命的“三结合”联合夺权的伟大方针。你们要同张国华同志和西藏军区革命领导同志合作，使“西藏地区的无产阶级文化大革命不走弯路”。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d1c2d79137","type":"paragraph","text":"此致","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"16f653654e","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命的敬礼","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5d12648493","type":"paragraph","text":" \t中央文化革命小组","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"742863a39b","type":"paragraph","text":"1967年2月24日","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"247358427c","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：《中央文件汇编》，拉萨革命造反总部，1969年3月。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"9804c6fe10","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}